{"tid":1789721,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【錢銀事小，分化事大】","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T14:16:22.000Z","uid":238693,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"54e1cda5047a00601a319a199f222ca30b3d80ae","tid":1789721,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"七千萬除二百萬人，每人一餐飯嘅錢，好快返來。<br />\n<br />\n星火出事最大危機係變成內訌，希望各位能夠轉一轉角度，唔係一味鬧星火唔小心，而係欣賞612嘅謹慎，一齊諗支援手足嘅出路，例如有冇機會將資源decentralize 去日漸成型的黃色經濟圈。我自己唔熟行唔識點做，但希望先拋磚引玉，唔同崗位都行多一步。<br />\n<br />\n由七月一日衝入立法會以來，我哋不斷中計，但不放棄每一位手足之下，總算能化險為夷，最少捱到黑警林鄭柒出國際。一齊行，就有機會將計就計。<br />\n<br />\n被捕手足已經多過全港獄中人士，我哋沒有分裂的本錢。"},{"pid":"f30276fbf50dc9af06ff3fd11534040f3bbcd275","tid":1789721,"uid":200624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d56471830a4b59c870dea259040c29424c37369","tid":1789721,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51171b11b46d4a6ec1330ac681fd765e1f423bd8","tid":1789721,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"11bed16bdc909e3efb556496e5d88d6e7a2afa24","tid":1789721,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44b2a3734230bdd07a83170dc8bb9412937dd5fa","tid":1789721,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">612是大家的希望</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799cbe8c27139d8da7bfe817f0c319bbef2af42c","tid":1789721,"uid":88940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"